name: Mike Chabot
description:
Info about the person:

Mike Chabot is an abundance coach, fitness trainer and Instagram model.

Note about the model:

This model was made by request of the @F000. It was trained on a dataset of 101 images, and this model also shows good results in the DeepFace tests. You can find the dataset (txt and img) of this model here.

It's too hot on Civitai, feel free to get me a drink or ask for a TI!
